products.title: Bulb
products.description: A bulb is an electrically powered device that produces light by passing current through a filament or a gas-filled chamber, commonly used for illumination in homes, offices, and outdoor spaces.

products.title: Tube light
products.description: A tube light is a type of fluorescent lamp commonly used for general illumination in various settings, emitting light through the excitation of mercury vapor within a phosphor-coated glass tube. Its long, slender design enables widespread and uniform lighting, making it popular in commercial, industrial, and residential environments.

categories.name: AC Motors
categories.description: AC motors convert electrical energy into mechanical energy through the interaction of magnetic fields, commonly used in various industrial and household applications.
